### 请求 /cps/platform/create 接口 => 成功
POST {{baseUrl}}/cps/platform/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

{
  "platformCode": "taobao",
  "platformName": "淘宝",
  "appKey": "DTK_TB_APP_KEY",
  "appSecret": "DTK_TB_APP_SECRET",
  "apiBaseUrl": "https://openapi.dataoke.com/api",
  "defaultAdzoneId": "mm_taobao_default_pid",
  "activeVendorCode": "dataoke",
  "supportedVendors": "dataoke,haodan",
  "sort": 1,
  "status": 1
}

### 请求 /cps/platform/update 接口 => 成功
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cps/platform/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "platformName": "淘宝联盟",
  "activeVendorCode": "haodan",
  "sort": 1,
  "status": 1
}

### 请求 /cps/platform/delete 接口 => 成功
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cps/platform/delete?id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/platform/get 接口 => 成功
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/platform/get?id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/platform/page 接口 => 成功
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/platform/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/platform/page 接口 => 按平台编码筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/platform/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&platformCode=taobao&status=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/platform/list-enabled 接口 => 成功
